'''天主教巴伊亞的聖萨尔瓦多总教区'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Sancti Salvatoris in Brasilia}}）是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[巴西|巴西]]设立的一个总教区。

其总主教享有“全巴西[[首席主教|首席主教]]”的头衔，主教座堂设于[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]的[[萨尔瓦多主教座堂|显圣容圣殿总主教座堂]]。總教区内350万人口中有70%为天主教徒（250万），下设109个[[堂区|堂区]]。現任總主教為[[思齊·達·羅恰|思齊·達·羅恰]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref name="Vatican20200311">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 11.03.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/11/200311b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-11 |language=en |date=2020-03-11 |archivedate=2020-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312034735/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/11/200311b.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pt|瑪爾谷·恩仁·加爾朗-萊特-德-阿爾梅達|Marco Eugênio Galrão Leite de Almeida}}和{{link-de|埃利奧斯·佩雷拉-多斯-桑托斯|Hélio Pereira dos Santos}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 25.09.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/09/25/0608/01358.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-03-11 |language=it |date=2013-09-25 |archivedate=2020-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312035155/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/09/25/0608/01358.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 27.04.2016 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/04/27/160427e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-11 |language=en |date=2016-04-27 |archivedate=2020-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312042359/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/04/27/160427e.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[吉拉·馬熱拉·阿涅洛|吉拉·馬熱拉·阿涅洛]]枢机和{{link-en|穆里洛·拉莫斯-克列熱爾|Murilo Ramos Krieger|穆里洛·施巴士坦·拉莫斯-克列熱爾}}<ref name="Vatican20200311" /><ref name="Miranda20010221">{{cite web |last1=Miranda |first1=Salvador |title=Consistory of February 21, 2001 (VIII) |url=https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/bios2001.htm |publisher=Florida International University |accessdate=2020-03-11 |language=en |archivedate=2020-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312035702/https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/bios2001.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

教区於1551年2月25日成立，从[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[天主教豐沙爾教區|豐沙爾總教區]]分设，1676年11月16日升格为总教区。

